zom=0.35 zom1=0.35 iN=input.getNumber iB=input.getBool oN=output.setNumber oB=output.setBool yx=0.0 yy=0.0 yh=0.0 PI=3.14159265359 kk=0 kkk=0 dis=0 UpDownPivot=0 LeftRightPivot=0 function clamp(x,d,u) if x<d then kj=d elseif x>u then kj=u else kj=x end return kj end function onTick() hre2=iN(1) cs=iN(2) vrdis2=iN(3) hrdis2=iN(4) GPSx=iN(5) GPSy=iN(6) vre2=iN(7) rtp=iN(8) alts=iN(9) UD=iN(10) LR=iN(11) UpDownpos=rtp-iN(12) rot=iN(13) zoom=iN(14) AutoAim=iB(3) --iB(1) and iB(2) radoff=not iB(3) --not iB(2) ciws=iB(3)and not (tfound and AutoAim) --iB(4)and iB(2)and not (tfound and AutoAim) wyj=(vrdis2+hrdis2)/2 if wyj*math.sin((vre2+rtp)*2*PI)>20 and wyj<800 then vre1=vre2 hre1=hre2 vrdis1=vrdis2 hrdis1=hrdis2 else vre1=0 hre1=0 vrdis1=1 hrdis1=0 end
if zoom>0.1 and zom<1 then zom1=zom1+0.01 end if zoom<-0.1 and zom>0.35 then zom1=zom1-0.01 end if iB(2)and not (tfound and AutoAim) then zom=0.35 else zom=zom1 end
if radoff then hre=0 vre=0 vrdis=dis hrdis=dis else hre=hre1 vre=vre1 hrdis=hrdis1 vrdis=vrdis1 end distance=(vrdis+hrdis)/2
Tdirec = math.fmod(-hre+cs+5.5,1)-0.5 Tpitch = vre+rtp hdis = distance*math.cos(Tpitch*2*PI)
x = hdis*math.sin(-Tdirec*2*PI)+GPSx y = hdis*math.cos(Tdirec*2*PI)+GPSy
h = distance*math.sin(Tpitch*2*PI)+alts
vx = x-yx vy = y-yy vh = h-yh
if vrdis ~= 0 and hrdis ~= 0 and math.abs(hre) <= 0.0625 and math.abs(vre) <= 0.0625then tfound=true else tfound=false end
if ciws then oN(7,-(math.fmod(rtp-0.07+100.5,1)-0.5)) LeftRightPivot=-0.125 else UpDown=(1.05-clamp(((zom-0.35)*1.53846),0.1,1))*0.3*(UD*3) LeftRight=(1.05-clamp(((zom-0.35)*1.53846),0.1,1))*0.3*(LR*3)
UpDownPivot=UpDown*0.1 if UpDownpos < -0.1 and UpDownPivot < 0 then UpDownPivot = 0 elseif UpDownpos > 0.23611 and UpDownPivot > 0 then UpDownPivot = 0 end LeftRightPivot = LeftRight * -0.1
if AutoAim and vrdis ~= 0 and hrdis ~= 0 and math.abs(hre) <= 0.0625 and math.abs(vre) <= 0.0625 then LeftRightPivot = LeftRightPivot - hre*10 UpDownPivot = UpDownPivot + vre*10 RB=true else RB =false end if math.abs(UpDownPivot)<0.000001 and AutoAim then oN(7,-(math.fmod(rtp-kkk+100.5,1)-0.5)) kk=kk+1 else if AutoAim then kk=0 oN(7,UpDownPivot) else oN(7,-(math.fmod(rtp+100.5,1)-0.5)) end end if kk<10 then kkk=rtp end end
if AutoAim then oN(8,LeftRightPivot) else oN(8,-(math.fmod(rot-0+100.5,1)-0.5)) end
if vrdis1~=0 and hrdis1~=0 and math.abs(hre1)<=0.0625 and math.abs(vre1)<=0.0625 then lock=true else lock=false end ook=45 en=5 accuracy=math.floor(math.sqrt((hre1*800)^2+(vre1*800)^2)/math.sqrt((0.0625*800)^2+(0.0625*800)^2)*100+0.5) if dis<4000 then g=50 r=0 else g=0 r=100 end
oN(1,x) oN(2,y) oN(3,h) oN(4,vx) oN(5,vy) oN(6,vh) oN(9,zom) oB(1,tfound) oB(2,iB(3)) oB(3,iB(2)and iB(5)) oB(4,tfound) oB(5,iB(7)) oB(6,iB(8)) oB(7,iB(6)) oN(20,UD) oN(21,UpDown) oB(8,tfound) yx=x yy=y yh=h end function onDraw() w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight() dx = 96/2 -ook/2 dy = 96/2 -ook/2 screen.setColor(60, 200, 0)
if not radoff then screen.drawRect(dx,dy,ook,ook) if lock then screen.drawCircle(96/2+hre1*360, 96/2-vre1*360, en) screen.drawText(96/2+hre1*360-5, 96/2-vre1*360-10, math.floor(distance+0.5))end end if radoff then screen.setColor(0,255,0,200) screen.drawText(40,37,math.floor(dis+0.5)) screen.drawCircle(48,48,5) screen.setColor(r,g,0,200) screen.drawLine(45,48,52,48) screen.drawLine(48,45,48,52) end end

ft=0 Eangle=0 ySGPSx=0 ySGPSy=0 ySalt=0 G=-30/3600 iN=input.getNumber iB=input.getBool oN=output.setNumber oB=output.setBool pgN=property.getNumber lmax=0.5 rmax=-0.5 umax=0.25 dmax=-0 vpm=1 Delay=10 FOV=0.9 NP=0
M=math abs=M.abs sin=M.sin cos=M.cos tan=M.tan asin=M.asin atan=M.atan sqrt=M.sqrt pi2=M.pi*2 pi=M.pi log=M.log fmod=M.fmod
velo=1000 DRAG=0.01
function atan2(y,x)ans=0 if y~=0 and x~=0 then if 0<y and 0<x then ans=atan(y/x)elseif 0<y and x<0 then ans=pi+atan(y/x)elseif y<0 and x<0 then ans=-pi+atan(y/x)elseif y<0 and 0<x then ans=atan(y/x)end else if x==0 then if 0<y then ans=pi/2 else ans=-pi/2 end else if 0<x then ans=0 else ans=pi end end end return ans end
function clamp(x,pm)if abs(x)>pm then if x<0 then return -pm else return pm end else return x end end function clamp2(x,d,u) if x<d then y=d elseif x>u then y=u else y=x end return y end
function Pc(x, pos)if pos<-0.0139 and x<0 then return 0 elseif pos>0.23611 and x>0 then return 0 end return x end
function Range(hdis, vdis) e = atan2(vdis,hdis) if -0.0872 > e or e > 1.48352 then return false end k1 = 3.0690153E-1*hdis k2 = -1.0135595E-3*hdis^2 k3 = 6.8255565E-7*hdis^3 k4 = -2.002029E-10*hdis^4 syatei = k1+k2+k3+k4+2019.4312 if syatei > vdis then return true else return false end end
function FlightY(Vo, tick) return (Vo-G*(1-DRAG)/DRAG)*(1-DRAG)/-DRAG*(1-DRAG)^tick+G*(1-DRAG)/DRAG*tick+(Vo-G*(1-DRAG)/DRAG)*(1-DRAG)/DRAG end
function FlightXTime(Vo,x)return -math.log(1-DRAG*x/Vo)/DRAG end
function Ssimu(x,y) DOWN = atan2(y,x) UP = clamp(DOWN+0.20944,1.5707)
for i = 1, 10 do AVE = (UP+DOWN)/2 Vx = velo/60*cos(AVE) Vy = velo/60*sin(AVE)
time = FlightXTime(Vx,x) Y = FlightY(Vy,time)
if Y < y then DOWN = AVE else UP = AVE end end
Vx = velo/60*cos((UP+DOWN)/2) ft = FlightXTime(Vx,x) Eangle = (UP+DOWN)/2
return 0 end
function onTick() output.setNumber(4,DRAG) output.setNumber(5,velo) Tx=iN(1) Ty=iN(2) Talt=iN(3) TVx=iN(4) TVy=iN(5) TValt=iN(6) CGPSx=iN(7) CGPSy=iN(8) Calt=iN(9) Cdirec=iN(10) SGPSx=iN(11) SGPSy=iN(12) Salt=iN(13) Ptilt=iN(14) Yawpos=iN(15) NumFireUnlock=iN(16) NumSwivelUnlock=iN(17) NumReload=iN(18) Ppos=iN(14) Find=iB(1) NP=NP
if NumFireUnlock == 1 then FireUnlock = true else FireUnlock = false end
if NumSwivelUnlock == 1 then SwivelUnlock = true else SwivelUnlock = false end
if NumReload == 1 then Reload = true else Reload = false end
SVx = SGPSx-ySGPSx SVy = SGPSy-ySGPSy SValt = Salt-ySalt
Tx = Tx + TVx*Delay Ty = Ty + TVy*Delay Talt = Talt + SValt*Delay
t = 0 for i = 0, 15 do hdis = sqrt((Tx-CGPSx+(TVx-SVx)*t)*(Tx-CGPSx+(TVx-SVx)*t)+(Ty-CGPSy+(TVy-SVy)*t)*(Ty-CGPSy+(TVy-SVy)*t)) vdis = Talt-Calt+(TValt-SValt)*t Ssimu(hdis,vdis) t = ft end
direc = atan2( -(Tx-CGPSx+(TVx-SVx)*t), Ty-CGPSy+(TVy-SVy)*t )/(2*pi) Eangle = Eangle/(2*pi)
YAC=(fmod(direc-Cdirec+100.5,1)-0.5) YNC=(fmod(Yawpos-NP+100.5,1)-0.5) YRC=(fmod(Yawpos+100.5,1)-0.5)
if iN(19)<lmax and iN(19)>rmax then tdirecy=true else tdirecy=false end if Eangle<umax and Eangle>dmax then tdirecx=true else tdirecx=false end
oB(1,not Reload and SwivelUnlock and Find and Range(hdis,vdis)and tdirecy and tdirecx and (iB(4)or FireUnlock))
if SwivelUnlock and Find and tdirecy then oN(1, clamp(YAC*8,0.5)*vpm) elseif Reload then oN(1, (-YRC*2)*vpm) else oN(1, (-YNC*2)*vpm) end
if not Reload and SwivelUnlock and Find and tdirecy then oN(2, Pc(clamp((-Ptilt+(clamp2(Eangle,dmax,umax)))*5,0.5),Ppos)) else oN(2,Pc(-Ppos,Ppos)) end oN(3,direc) oN(4,Eangle) ySGPSx = SGPSx ySGPSy = SGPSy ySalt = Salt end
